            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "id": 6433157,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 旭然(4556)急跌-6.12%報37.5元，成交697張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>旭然(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4556:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4556\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4556-TW</a>)近5分K跌速6.12%，27日09:16報37.5元，成交697張，今日跌幅為5.06％。（註：漲跌速為5分K的漲跌幅）</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>旭然(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4556:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4556\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4556-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲20.61%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+49 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+59 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-10 張</li> <li>融資增減：-181 張</li> <li>融券增減：+1 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
